texts.text: >The battle lasted for a long time,
>until the only ones left
>are you and Pixie and the demon Boss.
So it all comes down to you and me...
Fuck! Because of you, now I have to start again from scratch!
But before that, I'm gonna fucking kill you!
[sys user_name]!
>You dodge the demon's all out attack by a hair's breadth,
>and cut it down with a single blow!
*Gasp*
>The Boss' giant body wavers and then collapses.
>Now you and Pixie are the only ones left standing.
What a brutal battle...
And this place... It's no different from the ruins outside now...
>Like Pixie said, the building has been turned into rubble...
>Mutilated bodies are riddled everywhere...
What's that?
Hey, you hear something?
>Thud!
Can it be?!
That sound!
You hear it too this time!
C'mon [sys user_name], let's find out where it's coming from!
>You dig into the rubble and find a few survivors!
We found them! They're alive! Yes!
What... Happened? The battle... Ow...
Akito!
Akito!
I finished the fight.
You're alive...!
That means you did it...
So... You did it...
Then it wasn't for nothing...
Hey! I found another survivor!
>You turn around to see a woman buried under some rubble.
I think we can get her out! Help me clear this rubble away!
>You are just about to make your way towards Pixie when...
Heh... Teehee... You're not getting out of this... Alive...
Huh?
>With a bang, the roof that was barely left standing starts to come down!
Game over, suckers... Arrrgh!
Shit! What the hell! This ain't good!
>The woman's body is crushed by the collapsing roof...
It's no use! Let's get outta here, [sys user_name]!
Back away.
Reach out your hand
>You turn around to make a run for it,
>but you are stopped by an intense pain in your ankle.
>You can't move...
OMG, your injury from yesterday...!
What the hell are you doing?! C'mon [sys user_name]!
You're gonna die!
[sys user_name]!!!!
Gotta make it!
>You feel your body move through the air
>As debris crashes down on the spot you were standing on...
Huh?
Akito?

*Cough*
You alright...? *Wince*
>The lower half of Akito's body is crushed under the rubble...
Akito, why did you...
Why?!
Akito!

*Chuckle*
Why...?
I wanted to challenge fate...
To change the fate of the person who changed mine...
It's okay... It's my fate...
What matters is you're alive...
>You remember how you were unable to change the fate of the world...
>How you all lost to fate...

That look on your face...
Is that... regret?

If it is, don't...
This... This is what we wanted...
If you didn't save Ryo yesterday,
we wouldn't even be able to avenge our loved ones...
We probably would've given up on the idea entirely and served the demons until we die...
But you... You gave us hope...!
What use is hope...?
No, I didn't...
You were looking for a place to die...
But we didn't want to see the one who showed us hope die...
But...
Isn't that a bit selfish?
Yes, it is selfish of us...
But...!
We found hope in a wasteland full of despair.
It is only natural that we would want to cling to it...!
>You avert your eyes
>from Akito's candid gaze...
To tell the truth, I remember your face....
You used to be one of the Liberators.
You're Newbie. You're the one who left the Liberators and became the leader of the Acolytes...
I was mad at what you did. I even wanted to track you down and give you a good beating.
But I came to understand what you intended to do.
How you chose to avoid the end of the world by becoming the "Dominator"...
You chose the hardest path of all...
If you were strong enough to do that, maybe you can
bring this wasteland of a world hope someday...
>With that, Akito's body goes limp...
Noooooo!
Akito...?
>Jabo gazes at you and Akito from afar, taking in what happened...
The bigger the hope inside one's heart, the bigger the void its absence creates.
[sys user_name],
yet another tragedy burdens your heart now.
And so many trials still await you.
But I do believe you will pull through and rise again,
for the sake of this world.
For your future, and mine...
